02:29.236 --> 02:30.889
MAN: WOO-HOO!

02:34.545 --> 02:36.025
I NEED BACK-UP, ASAP.

02:36.156 --> 02:37.418
THERE'S A GUY
IN FRONT OF MY TOWER.

02:37.548 --> 02:38.549
HE'S ON A MOTORCYCLE.

02:39.159 --> 02:40.116
I DON'T KNOW WHAT HE'S HIGH ON,

02:40.247 --> 02:41.552
BUT HE'S GOING TO HURT SOMEBODY.

02:42.597 --> 02:44.120
HOO!

02:44.251 --> 02:46.166
[GIRLS CLAMORING]

02:48.733 --> 02:50.953
[LAUGHING]

02:52.911 --> 02:54.565
GET OFF THE BIKE NOW!

02:54.696 --> 02:55.958
GET OFF?

02:56.088 --> 02:57.307
SURE.

02:58.830 --> 03:00.832
STOP IT!
YOU'RE GOING TO HURT SOMEBODY.

03:04.662 --> 03:05.750
GET OFF, NOW!

03:07.404 --> 03:08.884
[RIDER LAUGHING]

03:11.452 --> 03:14.585
[ADVENTUROUS MUSIC]

03:34.997 --> 03:36.781
[WHINNIES]

03:42.961 --> 03:44.833
OKAY, HOMBRE,
YOUR RIDING DAYS ARE OVER.

03:49.533 --> 03:51.622
[SIREN BLARING]

04:08.030 --> 04:09.597
UH, JUST TAKE HIM AWAY
AND WRITE HIM UP.

04:09.727 --> 04:10.685
TURN HIM OVER TO GARNER.

04:10.815 --> 04:11.816
WHAT ABOUT HIM?

04:14.732 --> 04:16.255
I'LL TAKE CARE OF HIM.

04:22.392 --> 04:23.611
YOU DON'T HAVE TO THANK ME.

04:24.307 --> 04:25.308
I'M JUST GLAD
YOU DIDN'T GET HURT.

04:25.439 --> 04:26.918
THANK YOU?

04:27.049 --> 04:28.616
I SHOULD HAVE YOU ARRESTED, TOO.

04:28.746 --> 04:30.095
FOR WHAT?

04:30.661 --> 04:31.967
YOU COULD HAVE HURT SOMEBODY.

04:32.663 --> 04:34.012
JUST LIKE THAT PUNK,

04:34.143 --> 04:36.493
RIDING IN HERE
LIKE THE LONE RANGER.

04:38.626 --> 04:39.844
YOU KNOW,
YOU'RE EXQUISITELY BEAUTIFUL

04:39.975 --> 04:40.845
WHEN YOU'RE ANGRY.

04:41.498 --> 04:42.847
ANYONE EVER TELL YOU THAT?

04:45.763 --> 04:46.677
ONCE.

04:47.765 --> 04:49.114
A LONG TIME AGO.

04:50.377 --> 04:51.552
WELL,
MUST HAVE BEEN A SENSITIVE,

04:51.682 --> 04:53.075
PERCEPTIVE KIND OF GUY.

05:00.735 --> 05:03.694
WELL, I WOULDN'T EXACTLY
CALL YOU "SENSITIVE."

05:03.825 --> 05:05.392
JOHN D. CORT.

05:06.349 --> 05:07.916
BUT PERCEPTIVE AS HELL.

05:10.310 --> 05:11.311
HOW ARE YOU, C.J.?

05:12.834 --> 05:14.183
OH, I'M TERRIFIC.

05:15.663 --> 05:16.707
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

05:17.360 --> 05:18.622
YOU DON'T LOOK TOO HAPPY
TO SEE ME.

05:20.972 --> 05:22.017
I'M NOT SURE.

05:25.368 --> 05:26.674
BUT I'LL LET YOU KNOW.

05:32.332 --> 05:33.550
SHE'LL BE OKAY.

05:34.421 --> 05:35.639
SHE'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

05:38.163 --> 05:39.556
[CROWD MURMURING]

05:39.687 --> 05:41.471
[SCATTERED APPLAUSE]

05:41.602 --> 05:42.777
THAT STUFF'LL ROT YOUR TEETH.

05:42.907 --> 05:43.691
HOW MUCH DO I OWE YOU?

05:43.821 --> 05:44.648
THAT IS RAD.

05:45.301 --> 05:46.302
RAD, MAN?

05:46.433 --> 05:48.260
-UHH...
-WOW.

05:53.091 --> 05:55.398
MANUEL, THE ARGENTINE GIANT?

05:55.529 --> 05:57.182
"DANGER, STAND CLEAR,"
STAND CLEAR.

05:57.313 --> 05:59.271
"PARENTS, WATCH YOUR CHILDREN."

05:59.402 --> 06:01.186
THAT IS WILD.

06:01.752 --> 06:03.058
I DON'T KNOW, PAL.
HE COULD EAT YOU.

06:03.188 --> 06:04.799
NAH.

06:04.929 --> 06:05.669
-LET'S GO CHECK IT OUT, COME ON.
-NO, NO, LET'S GO CH--

06:05.800 --> 06:06.714
WHOA NO, NO, NO, NO.

06:06.844 --> 06:08.237
COME ON.

06:08.368 --> 06:09.978
LOOK, I DON'T WANT
TO GO SEE THE GIANT,

06:10.108 --> 06:11.371
...I WANTED TODAY AND I WANT
TO GO SEE HIM, COME ON.

06:11.501 --> 06:13.373
-LOOK OUT, LOOK OUT.
-WHOA.

06:14.199 --> 06:15.853
COME ON, HE'S GOT TO BE
AROUND HERE SOMEWHERE.

06:15.984 --> 06:17.202
I DON'T WANT TO SEE THE GIANT.

06:17.333 --> 06:18.595
WHY NOT?

06:18.726 --> 06:20.075
'CAUSE I WANT TO TALK
TO THIS PIG.

06:20.205 --> 06:20.945
NO! COME ON,
WE'RE LOOKING FOR A GIANT.

06:21.076 --> 06:22.730
A GIANT'S NOT A PIG.

06:23.600 --> 06:25.036
THERE HE IS.

06:25.167 --> 06:27.212
THE MOST DANGEROUS,
MEANEST MAN IN CAPTIVITY.

06:27.343 --> 06:28.910
THAT'S WHY WE KEEP HIM CAGED.

06:29.040 --> 06:30.825
SO EVERYBODY COME IN.

06:30.955 --> 06:33.436
IT'S LIKE THE WILDEST DREAM
OF ALL,

06:33.567 --> 06:34.916
OR MAYBE A NIGHTMARE--

06:35.046 --> 06:36.091
AH, LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.

06:36.221 --> 06:37.658
NO! COME ON. LET'S GO IN.

06:37.788 --> 06:40.312
HOBIE, THERE ARE NO SUCH THINGS
AS GIANTS.

06:40.443 --> 06:42.793
YOU ALWAYS TELL ME
TO BE OPEN-MINDED ABOUT THINGS.

06:42.924 --> 06:44.447
IT'LL ONLY COST YOU
A BUCK TO GO IN.

06:44.578 --> 06:46.275
UHH, COST ME TWO BUCKS.

06:46.406 --> 06:47.711
ALL RIGHT!

06:48.451 --> 06:51.149
[CROWD MURMURING]

06:55.023 --> 06:57.634
OKAY, THIS IS THE ONE
YOU'VE BEEN WAITING FOR.

06:57.765 --> 06:59.636
GET READY, LADIES AND GENTLEMEN.

06:59.767 --> 07:02.160
THE MOST DANGEROUS MAN
IN CAPTIVITY.

07:02.291 --> 07:03.553
SO BE CAREFUL,

07:03.684 --> 07:06.469
BECAUSE HE CAN REACH OUT
AND GRAB YOU.

07:06.600 --> 07:08.340
YOU DON'T WANT TO GET GRABBED,
DO YOU?

07:08.471 --> 07:09.690
YOU DON'T WANT TO GET HURT,
DO YOU?

07:09.820 --> 07:11.822
SO GET READY,
TAKE A DEEP BREATH,

07:11.953 --> 07:13.998
AND ALL OF A SUDDEN
WE'RE GOING TO SEE

07:14.129 --> 07:17.611
MANUEL THE GIANT.

07:18.394 --> 07:19.526
[CROWD GASPING]

07:21.919 --> 07:24.226
[GROWLING]

07:36.238 --> 07:38.066
[CROWD SCREAMING]

07:41.678 --> 07:44.681
NEXT TIME,
YOU CHASE AFTER THOSE KIDS.

07:47.162 --> 07:48.468
YOU MORON.

07:53.647 --> 07:54.561
BE RIGHT BACK.

07:56.084 --> 07:57.128
STUPID.

07:58.434 --> 07:59.609
EXCUSE ME,
CAN I SEE YOUR PERMIT.

08:00.305 --> 08:01.219
AND WHO ARE YOU?

08:01.350 --> 08:02.612
MY NAME IS MITCH BUCHANAN,

08:02.743 --> 08:03.874
LIEUTENANT LIFEGUARD,
L.A. COUNTY.

08:04.005 --> 08:05.006
LET ME SEE IT.

08:07.312 --> 08:08.705
JUST SHOW ME YOUR PERMIT.

08:09.271 --> 08:10.185
[GENTLE MUSIC]

08:10.315 --> 08:11.447
YEAH.

08:13.318 --> 08:14.885
YEAH, I WAS HOPING--

08:22.719 --> 08:23.590
ALL RIGHT.

08:25.330 --> 08:26.854
THE SHOW, DID YOU LIKE IT?

08:26.984 --> 08:27.942
NO, I DIDN'T.

08:30.118 --> 08:31.685
HERE IT IS, I GOT IT, SEE?

08:32.250 --> 08:33.687
HERE'S YOUR PERMIT.

08:41.129 --> 08:42.217
COME ON, PAL, LET'S GO.

08:42.913 --> 08:43.957
DAD.

08:44.087 --> 08:45.612
NO, THERE'S NOTHING WE CAN DO.

08:45.742 --> 08:47.048
HE'S GOT A PERMIT.

09:00.148 --> 09:02.324
THE GUY'S LUCKY I DIDN'T
PULL OUT MY BRANDING IRON.

09:04.500 --> 09:05.980
IT'S GOOD TO HEAR YOU
LAUGH AGAIN, C.J.

09:11.376 --> 09:12.769
SO THE RUMOR'S TRUE.

09:13.422 --> 09:14.162
OH, MITCH.

09:14.292 --> 09:15.380
-HEY, BUDDY.
-BUDDY!

09:15.511 --> 09:16.817
HEY, OH.

09:16.947 --> 09:17.948
-GOOD TO SEE YOU.
-GOOD TO SEE YOU, MAN.

09:18.079 --> 09:18.906
LOOK AT YOU, STAYING IN SHAPE.

09:19.036 --> 09:20.516
TRYING TO.

09:20.647 --> 09:22.692
SO WHAT'S THIS I HEAR,
YOU ARRIVED ON HORSEBACK?

09:22.823 --> 09:25.869
OH, HE'S GORGEOUS.
HIS NAME IS APACHE BOIER.

09:26.870 --> 09:28.655
YEAH, I WAS WORKING
THIS CARNIVAL OUT IN NEW MEXICO,

09:29.264 --> 09:30.352
THIS OLD COUPLE I KNOW...

09:31.832 --> 09:33.398
THIS JERK WAS DRUGGING THE HORSE

09:33.529 --> 09:35.139
TO KEEP IT CALM
BETWEEN SHOWS SO,

09:35.792 --> 09:37.141
TOOK THE GUY
BEHIND THE STANDS ONE NIGHT,

09:37.272 --> 09:38.403
GAVE HIM AN OFFER
HE COULDN'T REFUSE

09:38.534 --> 09:40.449
AND VOILA, APACHE WAS MINE.

09:41.102 --> 09:43.583
BRINGING HIM THE COAST
TO A FRIENDLY RANCH IN MALIBU.

09:44.584 --> 09:45.715
THAT'S QUITE A RESCUE.

09:46.237 --> 09:48.370
WELL, YOU KNOW ME,
LIFEGUARDING'S IN MY BLOOD.

09:48.979 --> 09:51.286
SO OBVIOUSLY YOU'RE BACK
FOR YOUR MANDATORY TEN DAYS.

09:51.895 --> 09:52.853
THAT'S TRUE.

09:53.418 --> 09:54.463
AMONG OTHER THINGS.

09:55.682 --> 09:56.813
WELL, YOU'RE IN LUCK.

09:56.944 --> 09:58.467
LIFEGUARD RECHECK IS TOMORROW.

09:59.033 --> 10:00.643
I'VE ALWAYS HAD GREAT TIMING,
HAVEN'T I?

10:01.296 --> 10:02.297
NO.

10:02.906 --> 10:04.386
HEY, CORT, MAN, GOOD TO SEE YOU.

10:04.516 --> 10:05.605
HEY, NEWMIE.

10:11.045 --> 10:12.089
WARM GUY.

10:13.917 --> 10:16.093
SO MITCH,
IF THE RECHECK IS TOMORROW,

10:16.790 --> 10:18.400
CAN'T AFFORD TO LET ALFALFA
GROW UNDER MY FEET.

10:18.922 --> 10:20.010
WHAT DO YOU SAY
YOU TOSS ME A TOWER?

10:20.141 --> 10:21.533
YOU GOT IT.

10:22.273 --> 10:24.145
WHAT DO YOU SAY
YOU JOIN ME FOR A WORKOUT?

10:27.191 --> 10:29.324
HEY, HEY, HEY, WHOA, BUDDY.

10:29.454 --> 10:31.761
YOU BETTER GET STARTED SOON,
YOU ARE LOSING IT.

10:32.936 --> 10:34.285
-YEAH.
-YOU ALL RIGHT?

10:34.895 --> 10:35.852
YEAH, I'M OKAY.

10:36.592 --> 10:37.724
I'M OKAY.

10:39.769 --> 10:41.162
YOU GOING TO GO SURFING TODAY,
DUDE?

10:41.292 --> 10:43.207
NO WAY, MAN.
THE WAVES ARE WAY TOO SMALL.

10:43.338 --> 10:44.600
THAT WOULD BE COOL, MAN.

10:44.731 --> 10:45.688
NO WAY.

10:45.819 --> 10:46.689
WHY NOT?

10:46.820 --> 10:48.169
'CAUSE THE WAVES STINK.

10:48.299 --> 10:49.518
THEY BE RAD, MAN.

10:52.303 --> 10:53.522
WHOA. LOOK AT THESE FOOTPRINTS.

10:53.653 --> 10:54.871
MAN, THEY'RE HUGE.

10:55.002 --> 10:56.612
MAN!

10:57.569 --> 10:58.527
OH, LET'S FOLLOW THEM.

10:58.658 --> 10:59.615
-YEAH.
-ALL RIGHT.

11:00.137 --> 11:01.835
SEE WHERE THEY GO.

11:12.715 --> 11:13.934
[BOYS SCREAMING]

11:16.371 --> 11:17.633
DUDE, A LIVE PELICAN!

11:17.764 --> 11:19.200
GET OUT OF HERE!

11:19.330 --> 11:21.768
GUYS, STOP! HEY!
COME ON! I KNOW HIM!

11:23.073 --> 11:24.335
[MUMBLING]

11:24.901 --> 11:25.728
WHAT?

11:25.859 --> 11:27.164
I SAID HOLD HIM STILL.

11:27.295 --> 11:29.384
CAN YOU CUT THE PLASTIC
OFF HIS LEG?

11:29.514 --> 11:30.733
SURE.

11:34.694 --> 11:35.738
YOU'LL BE FREE SOON.

11:40.917 --> 11:41.962
HE'S GOING TO BE OKAY.

11:42.092 --> 11:43.180
THANKS.

11:46.444 --> 11:47.707
I LOVE THE PELICANS.

11:48.751 --> 11:49.796
MY NAME'S HOBIE.

11:49.926 --> 11:51.188
I'M MANNY.

11:51.319 --> 11:52.886
YOUR FRIENDS WERE AFRAID.
WHY WEREN'T YOU?

11:53.625 --> 11:55.410
I SAW YOU AT THE PIER.

11:55.540 --> 11:58.021
WHY DO YOU DO ALL THAT STUFF
IN THE CAGE AND ALL?

11:58.152 --> 11:59.849
I HAVE TO. IT'S MY JOB.

12:01.198 --> 12:02.678
YOU WANT TO HELP ME
TO LET HIM GO?

12:02.809 --> 12:03.810
SURE.

12:09.990 --> 12:11.208
DON'T BE SCARED.

12:19.303 --> 12:20.827
HE'S HAPPY NOW.

12:23.960 --> 12:24.787
MANNY.

12:24.918 --> 12:27.007
MANNY, GET UP HERE.

12:27.137 --> 12:28.051
NOW!

12:29.313 --> 12:30.880
SORRY, I'VE GOT TO GO.

12:31.011 --> 12:32.664
WHY IS HE SO MEAN TO YOU?

12:32.795 --> 12:33.970
BYE, HOBIE.

12:42.065 --> 12:44.938
[POP MUSIC]

13:04.087 --> 13:06.873
♪ COME OUT FROM BEHIND
YOUR SHELL ♪

13:07.003 --> 13:09.658
♪ YOU KNOW
YOU CAN'T HELP YOURSELF ♪

13:15.142 --> 13:17.753
♪ DON'T YOU WORRY
