14:47.887 --> 14:50.280
♪ DON'T YOU FORGET WHO YOU ARE ♪

14:50.411 --> 14:53.327
♪ NO NEED TO DOUBT
I'M YOUR RIDE OR DIE ♪

14:59.811 --> 15:01.683
[GASPING]

15:07.689 --> 15:09.343
TWO VICTIMS! 2:00.

15:41.114 --> 15:41.941
HOW IS SHE?

15:42.071 --> 15:43.159
SHE'S UNCONSCIOUS.

15:43.899 --> 15:44.987
THERE'S NO PULSE.

15:46.423 --> 15:47.990
BABY! MY BABY!

15:48.121 --> 15:48.948
GET HER OUT OF HERE.

15:49.078 --> 15:50.862
[FRANTIC CHATTERING]

15:50.993 --> 15:53.822
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

15:53.953 --> 15:55.519
I WANT TO GO TO MY LITTLE BABY.

15:55.650 --> 15:57.304
OH, YOU CAN DO IT, COME ON.

15:57.434 --> 16:00.002
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

16:01.264 --> 16:03.223
OH, MY LISA BETTER BE OKAY.

16:03.353 --> 16:05.703
TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

16:08.880 --> 16:10.795
TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

16:11.927 --> 16:13.102
YOU CAN DO IT, COME ON.

16:13.233 --> 16:16.018
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

16:17.019 --> 16:18.629
COME ON, COME ON.

16:20.675 --> 16:22.459
OKAY. OKAY, BABY. THAT'S OKAY.

16:22.590 --> 16:24.331
THAT'S OKAY. COME ON. IT'S OKAY.

16:25.767 --> 16:26.855
YOU OKAY?

16:27.421 --> 16:29.292
SHE'S ALL RIGHT. IT'S OKAY.

16:30.076 --> 16:31.338
AH, GEEZ.

16:34.210 --> 16:35.516
AW, MAN.

16:36.386 --> 16:38.388
MOMMY'S HERE, HONEY.
MOMMY'S HERE.

16:38.910 --> 16:41.043
DON'T WORRY. YOU'RE OKAY, HUH?

16:43.828 --> 16:45.047
SHE'S GOING TO BE FINE NOW.

16:45.178 --> 16:46.744
[SIREN BLARES]

16:46.875 --> 16:48.485
HEY GUYS,
TAKE HER DOWN TO HEADQUARTERS.

16:48.616 --> 16:49.878
MAKE SURE SHE'S ALL RIGHT, HUH?

16:50.009 --> 16:50.922
RIGHT, MAN.

17:00.019 --> 17:01.803
NOW WE DIDN'T DO BAD TODAY.

17:03.587 --> 17:05.372
BUT IF YOU HAD BEEN SCARIER,

17:06.373 --> 17:08.243
THEN WE WOULD'VE MADE
A LOT MORE MONEY.

17:08.723 --> 17:13.380
I TOLD YOU, YOU HAVE TO RUN
AFTER THOSE KIDS.

17:15.556 --> 17:16.773
HEAR ME?

17:20.647 --> 17:22.040
YOU HEAR ME?

17:27.655 --> 17:28.525
HERE'S YOUR MONEY.

17:31.659 --> 17:35.793
DON'T YOU EVER PLAY WITH ONE
OF THOSE LITTLE BRATS AGAIN.

17:36.620 --> 17:38.405
ON THE BEACH, NO LESS.

17:39.667 --> 17:40.929
HE WAS FRIENDLY.

17:45.716 --> 17:47.675
YOU DON'T HAVE ANY FRIENDS.

17:47.805 --> 17:48.980
AND YOU DON'T NEED ANY.

17:49.590 --> 17:50.982
YOU GOT ME.

17:51.113 --> 17:53.115
I'M THE ONE
WHO TAKES CARE OF YOU.

17:54.073 --> 17:56.075
WHERE DO YOU THINK
YOU'D BE WITHOUT ME?

17:57.076 --> 17:58.468
I DON'T KNOW.

17:59.469 --> 18:00.557
I KNOW.

18:03.778 --> 18:04.692
NOWHERE.

18:05.693 --> 18:07.216
LOOK, DO WHAT I SAY.

18:07.347 --> 18:09.784
SCARE THOSE LITTLE BRATS,

18:09.914 --> 18:12.439
SO THEY GO TELL THEIR FRIENDS
ABOUT THE GIANT,

18:12.569 --> 18:14.963
'CAUSE THAT'S THE ONLY WAY
YOU'LL EVER MAKE A LIVING,

18:15.094 --> 18:16.704
YOU BIG OX.

18:22.710 --> 18:25.452
PELICANS, ALWAYS PELICANS.

