WE'LL TALK ABOUT YOUR TESTS.

30:58.769 --> 30:59.945
LET'S GO OVER HERE.

31:08.518 --> 31:11.304
THE BATTERY OF TESTS YOU TOOK
CONFIRMED ONE THING,

31:11.957 --> 31:13.349
