MY VISION'S--

31:17.223 --> 31:18.485
MY VISION'S 20-20.

31:19.181 --> 31:20.617
YES IT IS,
RIGHT IN FRONT OF YOU,

31:20.748 --> 31:22.663
BUT ONE OF THE PROBLEMS WITH RP

31:22.793 --> 31:24.012
IS THAT IT CAUSES TUNNEL VISION.

31:24.534 --> 31:27.886
THE NORMAL FIELD OF VISION
IS 180 DEGREES,

31:28.016 --> 31:30.845
BUT YOURS IS DOWN
TO JUST TEN DEGREES,

31:30.976 --> 31:32.629
TOP AND BOTTOM,

31:32.760 --> 31:33.935
AND THAT'S WHY YOU MISS
HAND SHAKES

31:34.066 --> 31:34.980
AND KNOCK THINGS OVER.

31:35.850 --> 31:38.026
WELL, WH-WHAT DO I--
WHAT DO I HAVE TO DO TO FIX IT?

31:38.679 --> 31:40.333
WELL, THE FIRST THING
YOU HAVE TO DO IS

31:40.463 --> 31:42.988
PROTECT YOUR EYES AGAINST
PROLONGED EXPOSURE TO THE SUN.

31:44.337 --> 31:46.687
NOW, I'VE GOT A PRESCRIPTION
FOR DARK GLASSES FOR YOU.

31:47.557 --> 31:48.907
UH, HUH.

31:55.130 --> 31:57.567
NO WAY, DOC. I'M A LIFEGUARD.

32:01.267 --> 32:02.703
