HER DECISION?

34:32.244 --> 34:33.158
NO.

34:33.853 --> 34:35.246
NO, IT HAS TO BE MINE.

34:37.900 --> 34:39.033
YOU KNOW WHAT'S FUNNY?

34:41.601 --> 34:43.123
I'M NOT GOING TO WORRY
ABOUT YOU.

34:45.431 --> 34:47.085
