34:48.956 --> 34:50.349
YOU'LL BE OKAY.

34:52.786 --> 34:55.049
WELL, I'LL TELL YOU ONE THING
I AM GOING TO DO WITH MY LIFE.

34:56.616 --> 34:59.184
I'M GOING TO APPRECIATE
EVERY SUNSET AND

34:59.314 --> 35:01.838
BEAUTIFUL THING THERE IS TO SEE.

